name: Feed Me (breadraptor)
description:
Music by Rory O'Neill
Art by Nancy McCollough, Logan McCollough, and Faythe Sabitus (donut)

Click and drag to feed the creacher an food. If you don't feed em fast enough, they'll die. If you feed em SUPER fast, you'll get more moola. Use moola to refill your food or buy a new creacher. Oh, and the wrong food will kill them too.

Press "S" to enable slow mode. Its easier and you gain a lot more money. :)
